{"tid":1673311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抵制TVB）消委會：森田面膜含致敏物 效能評分只獲2.5分","createTime":"2019-10-24T14:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T07:37:27.000Z","uid":75759,"like":134,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"ea67cadd9096dabe9b20968db5da91ea599879c9","tid":1673311,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:51:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>各位marketing JJ注意，<br />\nTVB係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">品牌負資產</span></span>，喺TVB落廣告，<br />\n你哋苦心經營嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">品牌形象將付諸流水</span></span>！無人可憐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB今個月開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到年底啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQ5Wz5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQ5Wz5d.jpg&h=37c5c7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【點解搞森田？】<br />\n森田藥粧喺TVB落廣告之餘，仲有份贊助TVB節目同請TVB偽人代言，所有可以俾錢TVB賺嘅佢都做齊！<br />\n<br />\n之前聽啲絲打講森田面膜唔好用，原來係真㗎！佢啲面膜竟然<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>含有致敏物！效果唔好之餘仲有機會影響皮膚健康</strong></span>！學肥mum話齋，你唔好害人啲仔女啦！敏感膚質嘅絲打真係多得你唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n藥監局：面膜含菌量嚴重超標 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lV61D9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lV61D9&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=a6d1bcb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2lV61D9</a><br />\n「24小時持續高保濕」誇大  <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lXGCbR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lXGCbR&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5f3d7062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2lXGCbR</a><br />\n消委會：森田面膜含致敏物<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/hotpick/20170418/1492512427716/【消委報告-保濕面膜參差】10元以下面膜有咩揀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fhotpick%2F20170418%2F1492512427716%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E4%BF%9D%E6%BF%95%E9%9D%A2%E8%86%9C%E5%8F%83%E5%B7%AE%E3%80%9110%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E8%86%9C%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E6%8F%80&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=e1f2f6f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fhotpick%2F20170418%2F1492512427716%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E4%BF%9D%E6%BF%95%E9%9D%A2%E8%86%9C%E5%8F%83%E5%B7%AE%E3%80%9110%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E8%86%9C%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E6%8F%80&h=a2b9ec14\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/hotpick/20170418/1492512427716/【消委報告-保濕面膜參差】10元以下面膜有咩揀</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">森田藥粧 Dr. Morita高純度玻尿酸潤澤面膜 Hyaluronic Acid Facial Mask\n\n每盒/每包約售：＄52（$5.2），保濕效能：2.5分［含致敏物「甲酯」（methylparaben）］</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n正所謂一不做二不休，既然森田一路唔撤TVB廣告，咁我地就罷買佢旗下全線產品，明確傳達我地香港人嘅立場！五大訴求，缺一不可<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">再唔撤budget，業績定仆直！盡快同TVB割席！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 任務流程】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是晚重溫@24 Oct 2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dr.moritahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdr.moritahk%2F&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=b23ee9c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dr.moritahk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請用幾秒去派嬲、留言、推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n※請善用template，清晰表達訴求，歡迎創意留言 <br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家用呢幅圖留言(建議直接貼圖片網址，有啲專頁ban左貼圖功能)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMez6h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMez6h1.jpg&h=f3752930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你想同致敏物零距離接觸嗎？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－<br />\n更多: TVB廣告客戶名單<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JSJaQK&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=b7a38d99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK</a> <br />\n<br />\n請即follow:<br />\nFacebook: #sayno2tvb<br />\nInstagram: @sayno2tvb<br />\nTG 頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=865c4747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 記者位置狙擊: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=d62770d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoretvb</a>"},{"pid":"70608dab4d240ef7e9862a1939a2ac3d26b0dd26","tid":1673311,"uid":188233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:51:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"040e2c92c9108ebd1e2df14043ba0a241c220c72","tid":1673311,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbYpESe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbYpESe.jpg&h=6c0e53db&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"948dc972153d03786241de91e7d938f61c7c74b4","tid":1673311,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:52